{"tid":2278140,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"近排發覺老婆朝朝都有人渣車接佢翻工","createTime":"2020-11-09T03:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T05:14:41.000Z","uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fee5ccd85c2d639f1c4f6aa5f4dd1ff06ed8f2a8","tid":2278140,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小妹平時搭巴士翻工，而老波就行去搭鐵。近排無意中發現老波朝朝翻工都行過兩個街口上左部C200。咁我就問佢乜事啦，佢話公司有個同區同事買左部車，咁咪朝朝車埋幾個同區同事一齊翻工順便慳下油錢囉。<br />\n老老實實，我就唔係幾信，但暫時見佢都冇乜位比小妹捉到，唔知各絲打有咩高見點去起清成件事。"},{"pid":"a1e20a35acaf803c03d20ca011250d621d0ad390","tid":2278140,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"唔玩膠出認真post了。情人節個晚同女友為左件禮物鬧交。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1883755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1883755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a695bcc26cf95ac46cc794ad802a6cc6c16a003","tid":2278140,"uid":182127,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"小妹&amp;老婆????"},{"pid":"4ea7f2e9f2fbc00297e1e14957a48a9ad20fcfda","tid":2278140,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a1e20a35acaf803c03d20ca011250d621d0ad390","tid":2278140,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"唔玩膠出認真post了。情人節個晚同女友為左件禮物鬧交。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1883755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1883755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"清咁得閒，連我自己都唔記得出過個咁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f73995b438994f85842d465cc89669e632613e","tid":2278140,"uid":257875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a695bcc26cf95ac46cc794ad802a6cc6c16a003","tid":2278140,"uid":182127,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"小妹&amp;老婆????"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"扮得女人多 改唔到口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heh